com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser

Class MobileBrowserBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jivesoftware.selenium.pagefactory.framework.browser.MobileBrowserBuilder

  • public class MobileBrowserBuilder
extends Object
    Created By amir.simhi on 8/20/14.

    Builder class for creating an App that is running on an emulator or a connected device that connected to the same host as the test code. Creates either a AndroidMobileBrowser, IOSMobileBrowser..

    A Browser is basically a wrapper for a WebDriver that greatly simplifies configuration, adds useful utilities, and has methods for loading Page's. Pages provide an object-oriented solution to Selenium testing. You can write Page classes that model a web page in the web app you are testing.
